OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1779210357
OL,3,CElla Toone and Luke Littler honoured
OL,4,Cby gongs for sporting achievements
OL,6,FTyldesley-born Toone is back in the
OL,7,Fnational ranks for the first time
OL,8,Fsince November after recovering from a
OL,9,Fstress fracture to her hip which
OL,10,Fruined the second half of her season.
OL,12,FThe 26-year-old said of realising she
OL,13,Fhad been picked for England manager
OL,14,FSarina Wiegman's squad: "We were
OL,15,Fsitting in the waiting room before
OL,16,Fgoing in and we quickly checked.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1779210357
OL,3,CElla Toone and Luke Littler honoured
OL,4,Cby gongs for sporting achievements
OL,6,F"Prince William asked if I was back
OL,7,Ffit and whether I'm on the next camp,
OL,8,Fso it was nice to be able to tell him
OL,9,Fthere. I am doing well and I've come
OL,10,Fback feeling better and stronger than
OL,11,Fever."
OL,13,FWatch Ella Toone receiving her MBE at
OL,14,FWindsor Castle
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1779210357
OL,3,CElla Toone and Luke Littler honoured
OL,4,Cby gongs for sporting achievements
OL,6,FToone, a double women's Euros winner,
OL,7,Fadded: "It is so exciting. There is so
OL,8,Fmuch talent in the England squad now,
OL,9,Fwith so many experienced players,
OL,10,Fplayers who've been to tournaments
OL,11,Fbefore, and loads of young, exciting
OL,12,Ftalent coming through as well.
OL,14,F"I am obviously really looking forward
OL,15,Fto it, and hopefully I can go out
OL,16,Fthere and represent England again."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
