OL,3,CElla Toone and Luke Littler honoured
OL,4,Cby gongs for sporting achievements
OL,6,FThe Lionesses, who have won all four
OL,7,Fof their qualifiers so far, travel to
OL,8,FMajorca for a crunch clash with
OL,9,Fcurrent world champions Spain on 5
OL,10,FJune, knowing a draw would be enough
OL,11,Fto seal their place at the tournament
OL,12,Fin Brazil.
OL,14,FToone spoke about how important it is
OL,15,Ffor the squad to act as role models,
OL,16,Fand cited it as a reason she set up
OL,17,Fthe ET7 Academy, a football coaching
OL,18,Facademy for girls aged eight to 19 to
OL,19,Fdevelop their skills.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1779210357
OL,3,CElla Toone and Luke Littler honoured
OL,4,Cby gongs for sporting achievements
OL,6,FShe said: "I set up ET7 Academy to
OL,7,Fgive girls a chance and an opportunity
OL,8,Fto play football, to make friends, to
OL,9,Fdevelop as people and players.
OL,11,F"I hope that one day we can have
OL,12,Fanother Ella Toone, who maybe comes
OL,13,Ffrom Tyldesley, where I grew up."As
OL,14,FLionesses, we are role models, we have
OL,15,Fgot to use our platforms as best we
OL,16,Fcan to really grow the women's game
OL,17,Fand to give all young girls and boys
OL,18,Fopportunities in football."
OL,26,@uD@aOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
