OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1779210357
OL,3,CElla Toone and Luke Littler honoured
OL,4,Cby gongs for sporting achievements
OL,6,FThe 19-year-old, currently ranked
OL,7,Fworld number one, is widely credited
OL,8,Fwith boosting the profile of the sport
OL,9,Falongside fellow darts great Luke
OL,10,FHumphries.
OL,12,FHumphries praised Littler for bringing
OL,13,Fa "massive new crowd" to darts as he
OL,14,Freceived his own honour from the
OL,15,FPrince of Wales in May.
OL,17,FWhen his MBE was announced in June,
OL,18,FLittler said: "To receive a
OL,19,Frecognition like this is something I
OL,20,Fhad never thought would be possible
OL,21,Fand it is a proud moment.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1779210357
OL,3,CElla Toone and Luke Littler honoured
OL,4,Cby gongs for sporting achievements
OL,6,F"It's unbelievable what I've done for
OL,7,Fmy sport. I'm happy, my family is
OL,8,Fhappy and I can't wait to receive it."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/9
